        | '(' tyvar '::' kind ')'       {% acsA (\cs -> (sLL $1 $> (KindedTyVar (EpAnn (glR $1) [mop $1,mu AnnDcolon $3 ,mcp $5] cs) SpecifiedSpec $2 $4))) }

fds :: { Located ([AddEpAnn],[LHsFunDep GhcPs]) }
        : {- empty -}                   { noLoc ([],[]) }
        | '|' fds1                      { (sLL $1 $> ([mj AnnVbar $1]
                                                 ,reverse (unLoc $2))) }

fds1 :: { Located [LHsFunDep GhcPs] }
